These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different games are played: whist, scrabble, domino, canasta, monopoly, poker, go
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person playing canasta##1
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is the argentine##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person playing domino##1
11. the person playing go is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Game           | monopoly | canasta | scrabble | domino | whist | poker | go |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

