.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
7 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, ferret, rat, hedgehog, hamster, dog
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Pet   | horse      | ferret   | rat   | hedgehog      | mouse       | dog       | hamster     |

