.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, turtle, guinea-pig, chinchilla, ferret
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the bartender is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the photographer##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Pet   | frog | guinea-pig     | hedgehog  | chinchilla       | bird       | ferret  | turtle   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

