.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There 7 different types of food: potato, peas, broccoli, asparagus, apricot, pumpkin, apple
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the person eating peas is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Food   | peas | broccoli | pumpkin     | asparagus | apple | apricot | potato |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

