.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
7 different games are played: chess, monopoly, bridge, poker, whist, canasta, scrabble
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, skateboard, tram, trike
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person playing chess is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Game    | bridge | canasta   | chess | poker | scrabble  | whist | monopoly |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

