.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, cola, tea, almond-milk, juice, lemonade
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, train
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person drinking cola is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Beverage       | fanta   | tea | lemonade | juice | milk     | cola | almond-milk |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi      | boat        | train         | helicopter | roller     | scooter |

