.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-10::.
There 7 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, orange, potato, pumpkin, strawberry, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, june, december, january, august, may, november
 1. the person eating potato is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Food   | pumpkin    | orange    | kiwi   | strawberry | grapefruit | watermelon | potato   |
| Birthday    | december | august | november | may  | march       | january     | june |

