.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-11::.
There 7 different types of food: lime, peas, pepper, potato, raspberry, spinach, tomato
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, red, turquise, aquamarine, yellow, mauve, emerald
 1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the far left##1
 3. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the person who likes red is the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person who likes red is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
12. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Food          | raspberry | lime     | spinach | pepper | peas      | tomato  | potato |
| Color   | aquamarine   | yellow | turquise  | red | blood-red | mauve | emerald   |

